@startuml
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam componentStyle rectangle

participant "开发者" as Dev
participant "配置中心\n(Nacos/Apollo)" as Config
participant "业务应用A" as AppA
participant "业务应用B" as AppB

Dev -> Config: 修改线程池配置
activate Config
Config -> AppA: 推送配置变更
activate AppA
AppA -> AppA: 动态更新线程池参数
AppA -> Config: 上报运行状态
deactivate AppA

Config -> AppB: 推送配置变更
activate AppB
AppB -> AppB: 动态更新线程池参数
AppB -> Config: 上报运行状态
deactivate AppB
deactivate Config

note right of Config
  **优点：**
  • 架构轻量，部署简单
  • 无额外中间件依赖
  • 运维成本低

  **缺点：**
  • 扩展性有限
  • 可视化能力弱
  • 功能相对单一
end note

@enduml